            Get more work done

          <p .content .is-normal .has-text-justified>  
            Smos' main goal is to help you get more work done.
            It is designed and optimized for power users.
            That means speed is one of the most important factors, which specifically means it is keyboard only, auto syncing, TODO_aanvullen
            Moreover, Smos follows the
            <a href=https://cs-syd.eu/self-management target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
